description: An amazing pairing of two Raging Stallion superstar exclusives: dark,musclebound, hirsute HUESSEIN and lanky, limber MATTHIEUPARIS! We were stunned the first time we gave HUESSEIN an ass toplunder with his beautiful, dark, able paws back in FISTPACK 5:ANAL TAP but there wasn't any way we could have been prepared forthe performance he serves up here when placed before MATTHIEUPARIS.
title: Fistpack 10 - Best In Hole, Scene #01
